                  </hi>. I am a seaman. I was in the prosecutor's shop, talk<lb></lb>ing to him across the counter—he started from the counter—I looked to the door, and saw the prisoner between the half-door and the bales of goods—he ran out—I followed him—he was stopped, and I gave him in charge.</p>
